Goal: Build a full-stack Progressive Web App (PWA) alumni platform for a school, with public school-focused content and a private alumni-only system with authentication, moderation, and job postings.

ğŸ”· TECH STACK

Frontend: React (Vite) + React Router

Backend: Node.js + Express

Auth: JWT-based authentication

Database: PostgreSQL (or MySQL)

Storage: Cloudinary (for profile & post images)

State: React Context for auth

PWA: Service workers, installable app

Styling: Clean, responsive UI (Tailwind or CSS)

ğŸ”· APP STRUCTURE

The app must have two clear sections:

Public (unauthenticated)

